A list of pages that are complete in content, but require Proofreading or formatting adjustments.

Please add pages to this Category that you feel have all content added, but may require more edits and/or formatting.

Should you find a page here that upholds quality standards, please remove this Category from those pages by deleting <code><nowiki>[[Category:Proofread{{#translation:}}]]</nowiki></code> from the page source. This marks them as "finished" for now.

A page does not need to have every detail ironed out to exit this Category, just enough to be presentable and digestible.